# How i reduced the file size of application file 
1) Remove all .tar file from html    (Through cammand line) 
   find . -type f -name '*.tar' -exec rm {} +

2) Remove all .zip file from html    (Through cammand line)
   find . -type f -name '*.zip' -exec rm {} +
